column16: Joc Pederson doubles (26) on a line drive to center fielder Manuel Margot.   Yasiel Puig scores.    Rob Segedin scores.
Josh Reddick pops out to shortstop Luis Sardinas.
Yasmani Grandal flies out to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.
Howie Kendrick walks.   Corey Seager to 2nd.
Justin Turner flies out to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.   Chase Utley to 3rd.
Corey Seager singles on a sharp ground ball to center fielder Travis Jankowski.   Chase Utley to 2nd.
Angel Pagan flies out to right fielder Hunter Renfroe.
Denard Span grounds out, shortstop Luis Sardinas to first baseman Wil Myers.
Ehire Adrianza lines out softly to center fielder Jon Jay.
Brandon Belt hits a ground-rule double (38) on a line drive to left field.
